OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Fdry evening with just a few light
OL,7,Fshowers possible. Mainly dry overnight
OL,8,Fwith some patchy low cloud spreading
OL,9,Finland. Best of the clear spells
OL,10,Facross Fermanagh and Tyrone.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FQuite cloudy at first but
OL,13,Fwith a few sunny spells. Cloud will
OL,14,Fgradually break up through the day to
OL,15,Fallow more bright or sunny spells.
OL,16,FRemaining dry and very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
