OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA dry
OL,6,Ffew days with long bright or sunny
OL,7,Fspells but the mornings starting
OL,8,Fcloudy, particularly around the east
OL,9,Fcoast. Very warm.
